<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.4.7">
<l>ilaimali paḷḷi yeyti yitumāya meṉṉa viṉamāya māṉpi ṉeḻilcēr</l>
<l>alaimali vēlka ṇāḷai yakalvippa taṟkō ruruvāya māṉai yamaiyā</l>
<l>kolaimali yeytu vitta koṭiyōṉi laṅkai poṭiyāka veṉṟi yamaruḷ</l>
<l>cilaimali ceñca raṅkaḷ celavuytta naṅkaḷ tirumālna makkō raraṇē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our one refuge is our divine Māl who sent many fiery arrows from [his] bow</l>
<l rend="indent">so that Laṅkā turned to ash,</l>
<l>When he went into battle conquering</l>
<l rend="indent">the discontented murderous, very evil one</l>
<l>Who caused a deer to appear in a unique form</l>
<l rend="indent">for capturing the beautiful lady with very agitated spear[-like] eyes,</l>
<l>As [she] thought, “This is a wonder!” having left a leafy hut</l>
<l rend="indent">[following] behind the deer which was in a herd.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
